name: Samira from League of Legends
description:
Samira from League of Legends

How to use

This is a LORA model which means that you will need to update A111's extension to latest OR use https://github.com/kohya-ss/sd-webui-additional-networks to combine the LORA with any model of your choosing.

My models are trained for weight 1.

Generating example images

See example images for prompts that will activate Samira & see the models I use. Samira will try to hold something by default, so use "holding" and "sword" in the negative if you don't prompt her to do anything. Remove "tattoo" and keep "arm tattoo" (I think "tattoo" is adding a womb tattoo for anime models lol)
